{"tid":1814220,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連登每日風向：泛民唔屌得，捉鬼唔屌得，嘉年華都係兄弟爬山，退場非勇武。","createTime":"2020-01-06T23:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T23:55:04.000Z","uid":40072,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"52b8fb88bc8aa58c2cd7d34c820add129365490c","tid":1814220,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:06:20.000Z","msg":"運動初期都冇咁多泛民打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家燒山、細良當咗大台聽佢地捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪冇人記得14年咩事？除咗所謂分化問題，仲有係嘉年華派膠令前線灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我而家先知原來勇武係一定唔會灰，一定唔係退場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難怪岳巴話你地係紙上談兵嘅趙括。<br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍司好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca9b344743927d98f8208fc91fdd96cbffc2df2","tid":1814220,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:19:09.000Z","msg":"啱啱上水無人捉鬼啦,打咩草人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffe5953f34bf551c52ad9b9aa115fc24606f937","tid":1814220,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bca9b344743927d98f8208fc91fdd96cbffc2df2","tid":1814220,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:19:09.000Z","msg":"啱啱上水無人捉鬼啦,打咩草人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:28:15.000Z","msg":"你點睇到捉鬼係草人，係重點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7545ee93e58a5f4b48561335c1038ae695731c2","tid":1814220,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連燈主流意見根本係冷氣軍師<br />\n憑空想像"}]}